                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-139-off747 t18300527-139-crimeloc750"></join>. This pair of shoes hung at my door-post at half-past three o'clock; I saw the prisoner take them, and put them into his apron; I pursued, and saw him stopped by 
               <persName id="t18300527-139-person1178">
                  John 
                  Thomas
               <interp inst="t18300527-139-person1178" type="surname" value="Thomas"></interp>
